    <div class="container-fluid bg-white p-0">

        <!-- Page Header Start -->
        <div class="container-fluid py-5 page-header position-relative mb-5">
            <div class="container py-5">
                <h1 class="display-2 text-white animated slideInDown mb-4">Discipline</h1>
                <nav aria-label="breadcrumb animated slideInDown">
                    <ol class="breadcrumb">
                        <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="#">Home</a></li>
                        <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="#">Pages</a></li>
                        <li class="breadcrumb-item text-white active" aria-current="page">Discipline</li>
                    </ol>
                </nav>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Page Header End -->

        <!-- Discipline Start -->
        <div class="container-xxl py-5">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="text-center mx-auto mb-5 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.1s" style="max-width: 600px;">
                    <h1 class="mb-3">Our Discipline Policy</h1>
                    <p>We believe in fostering a respectful, safe, and productive learning environment, where students
                        are encouraged to follow the rules and regulations that ensure the success and well-being of
                        everyone in our community.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="row g-4">
                    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.1s">
                        <div class="discipline-item">
                            <h3 class="mb-3">Respect for Others</h3>
                            <p>We expect all students to show respect for their peers, teachers, and staff members.
                                Disrespect, bullying, or any behavior that disrupts the harmony of our school will not
                                be tolerated.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.3s">
                        <div class="discipline-item">
                            <h3 class="mb-3">Timeliness</h3>
                            <p>Students are expected to be punctual for all classes, activities, and appointments.
                                Consistent tardiness will be addressed to ensure that the academic schedule runs
                                smoothly.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.5s">
                        <div class="discipline-item">
                            <h3 class="mb-3">Academic Integrity</h3>
                            <p>Cheating, plagiarism, and dishonesty in academic work will not be tolerated. We encourage
                                students to uphold the highest standards of academic integrity.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.7s">
                        <div class="discipline-item">
                            <h3 class="mb-3">Proper Attire</h3>
                            <p>Students are expected to dress in a manner that reflects respect for the school, their
                                peers, and themselves. The school uniform must be worn appropriately at all times.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.9s">
                        <div class="discipline-item">
                            <h3 class="mb-3">No Tolerance for Drugs or Alcohol</h3>
                            <p>The use or possession of illegal substances, including drugs and alcohol, is strictly
                                prohibited on campus. Students found in violation will face serious consequences.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="1.1s">
                        <div class="discipline-item">
                            <h3 class="mb-3">Respect for Property</h3>
                            <p>Students are expected to respect the property of others, including school property.
                                Vandalism or the destruction of property will result in disciplinary action.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Discipline End -->

